values:
I'm Still alive. I've been just Padding around my friends house and his hotel room. I need to thank him for putting up with me. 

I'm going to though head back to bugging him about His hair and other things. 

Toodles.

Do I want to know what's on this site?

http://www.missyhyatt.tv/

Francine.. what's on your site? Considering it's with a Current(?) Porn Queen?
I doubt I ever mattered in the end. *sighs*

Ever felt like.. again your just fucking up? 

I give up.. I really do. I'm just going to stay hidden and hide my heart from anyone. I'm tired of it being hurt.

I wish I knew what to say right now. *sighs* I realy don't know what to say or do. it's always wrong anyways. 

Bah
Um Sean.. I saw that you left REALLY early this morning.. Please I'll phone you.. Don't tell anyone.

I was walking into the hotel and I heard something.. well I found This little Guy hiding. He crawled into my arms and well.. He's mine now! We're both thrown away so we belong together. His name is Fate. Because it was really like Fate brought the little guy to me.
Jo.. NEVER dress like this again. Please...

I. Give. Up. edit: I'm tired of being what you want me to be Feeling so faithless Lost under the surface I don't know what you're expecting of me Put under the pressure of walking in your shoes (Caught in the undertow Just caught in the undertow) Every step that I take is Another mistake to you
Have you ever sat back and waited.. Your just waiting for the rest of the roof to fall on your head.

Fuck this bullshit. 

Matthew.. I Have a gift for you. A big one.. 

Kevin.. Yeah I lost my bestfriend over this. But thanks for everything.
Who do I get to kick?

HAPPY NEW YEAR!

I'm going back to cuddling with matt.
for you for you for you for you for you for you love
On a random note.. and NO I'm not having this problem.. how soon do you get morning sickiness?
I don't know what's going on. *sighs* i wish I did. I feel like shit.. I'm going to lay down. I've been sick.. just.. Yeah.
Matthew.. if you come on aim. Can you tell me. I'd like to talk .

*laughs* Everyone see the comercail? *grins* I thought it was funny.

Yes though.. Can we legally get married naked? *grins*
OH MY GOD.. I.. I .. I'm... *screams*

What happened.. why arn't Shawn and Kevin flaming around with thier Cute buts all in love.. 

*chews on her nails.*

Sorry I was kept VERY busy with Matt. 

I got wine, Chocolate Covered strawberries, his favorite Dinner and we curled up together. 

It was Perfect. Though Now I have to share him and Also go to pick up the secret gift. *grins*

Life seems to keep going on and on. Matt is perfect. I have plans for tonight.. 

Matthew.. *grins* Meet me in the Dinning room.

I'm feeling odd. With all these Rag Sheets saying I'm married to Peter. A fan Saw me and Matt. She waited until Matt left to pay for the food and walked right over. She had the .. *grits teeth* to call me a whore and told me I cheating on Peter. I just stoop up and left. I didn't tell Matt what was bothering me. I still haven't. 

I wish we didn't live in the public eye. I wish Rag Sheets could GET THEIR FACTS STRAIGHT. *sighs*

*smiles happily* I'm going to baby matt until he tells Me that I need to Bugger off. *giggles* I even found my old old Nurse outfit. *grins* Nurse Torrie *smiles* I think he needs something to drink so I'm going to run off.
I got you:This, , This, This, and this I hope you like them. :)

Perfect is curling up in Matt's arms and sleeping. 

Also it's really not caring what people think about you. Because as long as your happy with yourself. fuck the world. 

Matthew Moore Hardy... I love you. I'm tieing you to the bed and having my way with you though.

I've been watching him sleep. *sighs happily* 

Yes everything is a complete mess. But it'll get cleaned. Everything sorted and put right. It'll be what we both decided and I hope everything looks good. Though I do think he'll put his foot down about a pink bed spread. *laughs* 

I'm just happy to be here. To be here with him. 

Life is perfect.

I'm MOVING TO NC!

*screams and dies*

I'm moving in the beautiful, sexy, loving and perfect Matthew Hardy.

I could not be happier.
I think everyday He proves to me over and over why I love him so much. He's just.. perfect.

*shakes head* I have nothing to say at all. 

Matthew my dear. I have plans for you. Hot tub, wine and naked Hardy.. Sounds like a perfect evening. Tomorrow?

I woke up and.. *sighs happily* I'm still just floating on air. 

I guess I owe everyone phone calls huh? 

Kevin are you ok?

Matthew... *BIG kisses*
